channel.title: Kingdom hearts birt by sleep
channel.description:
I am a HHHUUGGEE kingdom hearts fan. and i cant wait till the new kingdom hearts birth by sleep comes out on the psp. so does any 1 have a scientific guess on when the title gets released? some facts on earlier title releases. ------------------------------------------------------- KH1: jp:March 28 2002 us:September 17 2002 ------------------------------------------------------- KH chain of mem: jp:November 11 2004 us:December 7 2004 ------------------------------------------------------- KH2: jp:Decembered 22 2005 us:March 28 2006 ------------------------------------------------------- KH RE:chain of mem: jp:March 29 2007 us:December 2 2008 -------------------------------------------------------
and the team that did RE: chain of memories are working on birth by sleep. so we might have a loonngg wait =\
